  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At level 7, you can recall your bodyguard even if they have already been defeated by using the special seal applied to them.<br />Your bodyguard will reappear within 5 ft of your position with half of their max HP and half of their chakra.<br />After combat, your bodyguard will suffer 3 exhaustion points, which will be reduced by 1 per long rest or fully recovered during a full rest.<br />These exhaustion points cannot be cured or reduced by any means except by the bodyguard's own traits.<br />You can only recall your bodyguard once per full rest or after they have recovered from all of their exhaustion points.</p>",
